{
"#name"
:
{
"gg"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"Google Gemini AI 搜索工具"
,
"en"
:
"Google Gemini AI search tool"
}
,
"#keyword"
:
[
"gemini cli"
,
"google gemini AI"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Search the web using Google Gemini AI. Combines Google Search with AI-generated answers.\nSupports multiple output formats (markdown, raw), source citation, and model selection.\nResults are cached for 1 hour by default.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 Google Gemini AI 进行网络搜索。结合 Google 搜索和 AI 生成的答案。\n支持多种输出格式（Markdown、原始文本）、来源引用和模型选择。\n结果默认缓存 1 小时。\n"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x gg \"<question>\""
:
null
}
,
{
"x gg --md \"<question>\""
:
null
}
,
{
"x gg --raw \"<question>\""
:
null
}
,
{
"x gg --source \"<question>\""
:
null
}
,
{
"x gg --model <model> \"<question>\""
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Output modes:\n--md: Markdown format (default in TTY)\n--raw: Plain text without formatting\n--source: Include source URLs (default: concurrent mode)\n--source-detail: Include source with content preview\n--source-raw: Include source URLs only\n--no-source: No source URLs\n\nModels: gemini-2.5-pro, gemini-2.5-flash, gemini-2.0-flash\nProviders: gemini (default), hub\n"
,
"cn"
:
"输出模式：\n--md：Markdown 格式（TTY 默认）\n--raw：无格式纯文本\n--source：包含来源 URL（默认并发模式）\n--source-detail：包含来源及内容预览\n--source-raw：仅包含来源 URL\n--no-source：不包含来源 URL\n\n模型：gemini-2.5-pro、gemini-2.5-flash、gemini-2.0-flash\n提供商：gemini（默认）、hub\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg \"What is x-cmd?\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Search for x-cmd introduction"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：搜索 x-cmd 的介绍"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --no-source \"Who won the euro 2024?\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Search without source URLs"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：搜索 2024 年欧洲杯冠军，不显示来源链接"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --md \"Explain quantum computing\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get markdown formatted answer"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：获取 Markdown 格式的量子计算解释"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --raw \"Current bitcoin price\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get raw text output without formatting"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：获取无格式的原始文本输出"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --source \"Latest AI news\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Search with source URLs"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：搜索最新 AI 新闻并显示来源链接"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --source-detail \"Python tutorial\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Search with detailed source content"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：搜索 Python 教程并显示详细来源内容"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --model gemini-2.5-pro \"Complex math problem\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Use specific model for complex questions"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：使用特定模型处理复杂问题"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --model gemini-2.5-flash \"Quick answer\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Use flash model for faster response"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：使用 flash 模型获取快速响应"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --cache-time 5m \"Weather today\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set cache time to 5 minutes"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：设置缓存时间为 5 分钟"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --cache-time 1d \"Historical facts\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Set cache time to 1 day for stable content"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：对稳定内容设置缓存时间为 1 天"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x gg --provider hub \"Enterprise search\""
,
"en"
:
"Example: Use hub provider for enterprise search"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：使用 hub 提供商进行企业搜索"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"echo \"Explain this code\" | x gg --md"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Pipe text to gg for explanation"
,
"cn"
:
"示例：通过管道将文本传给 gg 进行解释"
}
]
,
"--md"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 Markdown 格式输出结果"
,
"en"
:
"Output results in Markdown format"
}
}
,
"--raw"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出原始数据，无格式"
,
"en"
:
"Output raw data without formatting"
}
}
,
"--source"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出搜索结果来源的网络链接（并发获取详情）"
,
"en"
:
"Output source URLs with concurrent detail fetching"
}
}
,
"--source-detail"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出搜索结果来源及详细内容"
,
"en"
:
"Output source URLs with detailed content preview"
}
}
,
"--source-raw"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"只输出搜索结果来源链接"
,
"en"
:
"Output source URLs only"
}
}
,
"--no-source"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"不输出搜索结果来源的网络链接"
,
"en"
:
"Do not output source URLs"
}
}
,
